{"type":"message","id":"7f923930","parentId":"2f3469d9","timestamp":"2026-02-27T01:37:24.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定！**akshare-quant.skill** 已经打包完成。\n\n## 总结\n\n我创建了一个完整的 akshare skill，包含：\n\n### 📁 Skill 结构\n```\nskills/akshare-quant/\n├── SKILL.md                    # 主文档（使用指南）\n├── references/\n│   └── api_reference.md        # API快速参考\n└── scripts/\n    ├── get_stock_price.py      # 获取个股基本信息\n    ├── get_hist_data.py        # 获取历史行情数据\n    └── batch_query.py          # 批量查询多只股票\n```\n\n### ✅ 已测试的功能\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 个股基本信息查询 | ✅ 正常 |\n| 历史行情数据（日线） | ✅ 正常 |\n| 批量股票查询 | ✅ 正常 |\n| 新闻资讯 | ✅ 正常 |\n\n### 🎯 核心使用方式\n\n**查股价：**\n```bash\npython scripts/get_stock_price.py 600519\n```\n\n**查历史数据：**\n```bash\npython scripts/get_hist_data.py 600519 --days 30\n```\n\n**批量查询：**\n```bash\npython scripts/batch_query.py 600519 000001 000333\n```\n\n### ⚠️ 已知限制\n- 全市场数据（5000+股票）可能超时，建议单只或少量查询\n- Windows 控制台有编码问题，但不影响数据获取\n\n现在你可以用这个 skill 随时调取精确的量化数据了！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":52877,"output":307,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772156226713}}
