{"type":"message","id":"b05d6097","parentId":"0fe1bd44","timestamp":"2026-02-27T02:06:09.860Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！**playwright-browser.skill** 已经打包完成。\n\n## 总结\n\n我已经创建了 **3 个完整的 skill**：\n\n| Skill | 功能 | 状态 |\n|-------|------|------|\n| `image-recognition` | 图片识别、OCR | ✅ 已测试，可用 |\n| `akshare-quant` | A股/基金/指数数据获取 | ✅ 已测试，可用 |\n| `playwright-browser` | 浏览器自动化控制 | ✅ 已测试，可用 |\n\n### Playwright MCP 的问题\n微软官方的 `@microsoft/playwright-mcp` 包由于网络/SSL问题暂时无法安装。但我们自己的 `playwright-browser` skill 已经可以：\n- 启动 Chrome 浏览器\n- 访问网页\n- 截图\n- 提取数据\n- 自动填写表单\n\n如果需要更高级的 MCP 集成，可以等网络问题解决后再尝试安装官方版本。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":69040,"output":191,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69231,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772157929640}}
